(10, 1, '2024-04-02 05:29:16', '2024-04-02 05:29:16', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":28,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/about-petani.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-28\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sukatani Village is a picturesque hamlet nestled amidst the lush landscapes of Indonesia, offering a serene retreat from the bustling urban life. Located in the heart of West Java, this quaint village charms visitors with its captivating blend of natural beauty and traditional Javanese culture. Surrounded by verdant rice fields and swaying coconut palms, Sukatani Village exudes tranquility and rustic charm.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The village is characterized by its traditional Javanese architecture, with quaint wooden houses adorned with intricate carvings and vibrant batik textiles. The warm hospitality of the locals adds to the villages inviting atmosphere, as visitors are welcomed with open arms and treated to authentic Javanese cuisine and cultural experiences.<br>Nature enthusiasts will delight in the abundance of outdoor activities available in Sukatani Village, from leisurely walks through the rice paddies to adventurous hikes in the nearby mountains. The village also serves as a gateway to explore the regions natural wonders, including waterfalls, hot springs, and lush forests teeming with wildlife.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For those seeking a glimpse into Indonesias rich cultural heritage, Sukatani Village offers traditional dance performances, gamelan music concerts, and workshops on batik making and traditional crafts. Whether youre looking for relaxation, adventure, or cultural immersion, Sukatani Village promises an unforgettable experience amidst the timeless beauty of rural Indonesia.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"50px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Vision Sukatani Village</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To preserve and promote the rich cultural heritage of Sukatani Village.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To establish Sukatani Village as a sustainable eco-tourism destination.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To empower the local community through tourism development.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"50px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Mission Sukatani Village</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To conserve the natural beauty and biodiversity of Sukatani Village.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To showcase traditional Javanese arts, crafts, and cuisine.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To provide authentic and immersive cultural experiences for visitors.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To support local livelihoods and economic growth through tourism initiatives.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>To collaborate with stakeholders for the sustainable development of Sukatani Village.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer -->\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->', 'Village Profile', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'village-profile', '', '', '2024-04-02 23:28:12', '2024-04-02 23:28:12', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=10', 0, 'page', '', 0),
